{"tid":635893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【科普笑話】啱啱諗到個火星探索的笑話","createTime":"2018-04-20T11:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T12:09:02.000Z","uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a92be2d7ad8c477017e5f5e16cf1aed4cd4c364","tid":635893,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"火星探索笑話一則<br />\n－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n小明是NASA的科學家，負責火星探索任務，每天從早到晚都在實驗室工作，沒到深夜也不回家。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的生活過了兩個月，小明的妻子終於忍不住，向他抱怨：「到底是你的火星任務重要，還是我重要？」<br />\n<br />\n這個問題，可能去計算火箭從地球去火星需要多少燃料會更簡單。<br />\n<br />\n小明沉默了三十秒，然後回覆：「火星任務比較重要！」<br />\n<br />\n小明的妻子聽了後頓時眼冒金星，正想向小明大吼之際，小明說：「因為...」<br />\n<br />\n「你快點說！」小明的妻子給他機會解釋。<br />\n<br />\n「因為在火星上，你的體重只有地球的38%\b。」<br />\n<br />\n聽罷，二人回睡房重新探研宇宙黑洞的奧秘。"},{"pid":"aacf7d190f2a4f1e61db78af8502199483923e43","tid":635893,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3168881ef627df68da24c654a4a628dd35e7127","tid":635893,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"Ok thanks"},{"pid":"67baa4e93874be0cd7fbfb79966eb15fc428a554","tid":635893,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a7f67b0ea357b24da2bb63f62fbc0b6fd6e4e1","tid":635893,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"2ee69a02389c01c064c1697e86fa811d3ce0c5bd","tid":635893,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67baa4e93874be0cd7fbfb79966eb15fc428a554","tid":635893,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}